0";s:6:"isroll";s:1:"0";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1522826277";s:9:"create_ip";s:14:"119.185.71.106";s:5:"views";s:3:"229";s:3:"zan";s:2:"10";s:10:"donate_num";s:1:"0";s:6:"closed";s:1:"0";s:7:"valuate";s:1:"0";s:5:"audit";s:1:"1";}i:3;a:25:{s:10:"article_id";s:2:"26";s:5:"title";s:51:"不可思议，原来我们每天喝的都是......";s:7:"cate_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"city_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"area_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"shop_id";s:1:"0";s:6:"source";s:0:"";s:8:"profiles";s:30:"山泉水和纯净水的区别";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:7:"orderby";s:1:"0";s:5:"photo";s:28:"2018/08/09/5b6c094509495.jpg";s:5:"audio";s:0:"";s:5:"video";s:0:"";s:11:"video_photo";s:0:"";s:7:"details";s:2183:"<p><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 夏季来临，水作为生命之源，毫无疑问，多喝水对我们的身体健康是非常重要的，但是，我们喝的水是“好水”吗？你知道山泉水和纯净水的区别吗？</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><img style="WIDTH: 355px; HEIGHT: 209px" src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c0398a3a44.jpg" width="498" height="325" _src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c0398a3a44.jpg"/>&nbsp; </span><strong style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="COLOR: #7030a0">山泉水&nbsp; </span></strong><span style="font-size:12px">取自于无污染的山区，然后经由“粗筛子”（超滤技术）过滤，将大分子的细菌和胶质物质过滤掉，保留以离子方式存在的矿物质等微量元素，然后杀菌、消毒。属大自然的天然水，最适宜人体功能需求</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c03e328ad0.jpg" _src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c03e328ad0.jpg"/>&nbsp; </span><strong style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="COLOR: #7030a0">纯净水&nbsp; </span></strong><span style="font-size:12px">是以自来水、地表水或地下水（易被污染）为水源，用“细筛子”（反渗透）过滤，将水中的细菌杂质以及对人体有益的微量元素都过滤掉了！也就是大家经常说的“</span><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70);font-size:12px">刮骨水</span><span style="font-size:12px">”。长期饮用会引起少儿发育不良，孕哺乳期妇女、老年人的各种微量元素缺乏症。</span></p><p align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 18px"><img style="WIDTH: 198px; HEIGHT: 167px" src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c0416c94c7.jpg" width="200" height="190" _src="http://www.enjoysix.cn/attachs/editor/2018/08/09/thumb_5b6c0416c94c7.jpg"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p align="left"><span>因此，养成良好的喝水习惯。多喝水，喝好水，身体健康自然会随之而来<br/>健康美丽，由放心水而生</span></p><p></p>";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:6:"isroll";s:1:"0";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1533806213";s:9:"create_ip";s:15:"119.183.113.215";s:5:"views";s:3:"191";s:3:"zan";s:2:"68";s:10:"donate_num";s:1:"1";s:6:"closed";s:1:"0";s:7:"valuate";s:1:"0";s:5:"audit";s:1:"1";}i:4;a:25:{s:10:"article_id";s:2:"28";s:5:"title";s:68:"六享山泉水招募合伙人啦| 确认过眼神，你是对的人";s:7:"cate_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"city_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"area_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"shop_id";s:1:"3";s:6:"source";s:12:"六享生活";s:8:"profiles";s:17:"合伙人招募
